WEBVTT

00:04:59.037 --> 00:05:00.209
reach,

00:05:00.233 --> 00:05:02.549
this idea that the temple
could have reach,

00:05:02.573 --> 00:05:04.345
like this reach for the divine.

00:05:05.407 --> 00:05:07.232
You can imagine also

00:05:07.256 --> 00:05:12.151
that movement within a circle
could mean movement and stillness,

00:05:12.175 --> 00:05:14.166
like the cosmos,

00:05:14.190 --> 00:05:16.834
something you see in many places.

00:05:17.885 --> 00:05:20.287
(Laughter)

00:05:20.311 --> 00:05:23.626
But rotation was not enough,

00:05:24.848 --> 00:05:27.032
because we needed a form.

00:05:27.056 --> 00:05:29.322
In the Bahá'í writings, it talks about

00:05:29.346 --> 00:05:34.208
the temples being as perfect
as is humanly possible,